fno: In the cash market, the Nifty 50 declined 85.60 points or 0.45% to settle at 18,771.25. The NSE's India VIX, a gauge of market's expectation of volatility over the near term, advanced 2.25% to 11.55. HDFC Bank, ICICI Bank, Infosys were the top traded individual stock futures contracts in F&O segment of NSE. The June 2023 F&O contracts will expire on 29 June 2023.
